Python based 2D Side-Scroller game.

Inital Plot:
The year is 2099, and humanity has been forced into a retreat from across the globe into densely packed strongholds from the robot uprising,
where robotic slaves turned against their masters and creators.
You are part of Mecha Force, and organisation designed to fight against attacks on the strongholds.
However, on your patrol by the outer wall (tutorial mission) you discover a plan in action by to robots to destroy the humans!
With no time to waste, it's up to you to stop it.
-WAD to move:
  W to jump
  A to move backwards
  D to move forwards
 -Space to fire projectile.
 -Mouse pointer to aim.
 -Up/Down Arrows to switch weapon when appropriate.
